    2. components
    3. carousel

    Slide Only

    A slideshow component for cycling through elements—images or slides of text—like a carousel. Read bootstrap documentaion for more details.

    With controls

    Adding in the previous and next controls. Read bootstrap documentaion for more details.

    Previous Next

    With Indicators

    You can also add the indicators to the carousel, alongside the controls, too. Read bootstrap documentaion for more details.

    Previous Next

    With Captions

    Add captions to your slides easily with the .carousel-caption element within any .carousel-item. Read bootstrap documentaion for more details.
